name: Martins First
description:
Very laid back and easy to be around. Outstanding sense of humor. I make everyone feel comfortable and also seem to have the nack for making people laugh and feel good about themselves. I believe there is something good in everyone. Would like to find a lady that is capable of giving love……and receiving it as well. Please be real.
Being honest here….I’m not sure I see much need for endless emails. If you think you might have an interest just let me know and we can exchange a few emails and then meet. I’m really here to find someone meaningful. I have a goal and hopefully you do too. Thx
